{"lemma":"مُحِيطُو","slug":"مُحِيطُو","root":"ح.#.ط","root_slug":"ح-_-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-_-ط","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مُحِيط","root":"حوط","pos":"N","occurrence_count":9},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9539"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%AD%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B7%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"whole"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"overall"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"thorough"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ocean"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"surroundings"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"environment"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"circumference"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"perimeter"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"entourage"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb أَحَاطَ (ʔaḥāṭa, “to surround, enclose, contain, encircle, know completely”)."},"ipa":["/mu.ħiːtˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9539","headword_ar":"مُحِيطٌ","root":"HwT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[act. part. n. of 4;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Surrounding, encompassing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enclosing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] ―         -b2-  It is said in the Kur [lxxxv. 20],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@ll~`hu mino waraAy^ihimo muHyiTN","text_ar":"وَا@للّٰهُ مِنْ وَرَايِهِمْ مُحيِطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And God, behind them, includeth them altogether within his power; not one shall escape Him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And again, [xi. 85,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea*aAba yawomK muHiyTK","text_ar":"عَذَابَ يَوْمٍ مُحِيطٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The punishment of a day which shall beset on every side so that there shall be no place of escape from it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a destructive day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning the day of resurrection: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the punishment"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a day"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of extermination:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the epithet, which is that of the punishment, being applied to the day because it includes it. (Bd.) And again, [ii. 18,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@ll~`hu muHiyTN biAlkaAfiriyna","text_ar":"وَا@للّٰهُ مُحِيطٌ بِالكَافِرِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained by Mujá- hid as signifying (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And God will collect together the unbelievers"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the day of resurrection. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}